Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:42.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:49.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:01.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:06.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:12.13,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:17.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:22.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:34.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:45.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:51.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:42.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果將來能和你一起實現那永恆的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:49.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能夠變強 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:01.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有預告的奇跡邂逅 是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:06.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守護你 再也不會孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:12.13,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:17.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:22.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保證 一定會去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:28.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法觸及的明天 高高在上無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:34.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的現實讓願望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恆的夢中期盼光明來臨的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:45.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會到達那裏 現在就穿越時空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:51.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:55.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我將與你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:16.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:22.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:35.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:41.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:46.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:52.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:03.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:07.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:14.17,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:18.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:24.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.78,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:37.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:16.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠守護你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:22.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會變得更強大 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:35.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,讓心情馳騁起來 超越各種危機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:41.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會馬上就讓你覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:46.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,曖昧弱小的心需要超越極限的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:52.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能捕捉到你的信號 我準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:57.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為比誰都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:03.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情不斷高漲 來吧 用這個心情去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:07.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的夢想 你的明天 你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:14.17,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓一定用這雙手來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:18.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你拭去所有的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:24.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好擔心啊 但是你的笑容又讓人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.90,0:23:27.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:32.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因為因為 要變得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:37.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更強更強 幼獅雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和師父一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以KnightLancer是玉鳳的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很榮幸 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是你的願望 那麼我就成為你的父親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來你就是我的女兒了 我是你的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你需要的時候 身為父親無論何時何地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都將趕到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸？我是..父親？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer他最後怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他幫助了女孩子 然後那位女孩就..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？看你好像一整天都無精打采的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必去..騎士部那樣的地方..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不 那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事絕對不適合花房君的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會幫你一起說的 說服她們讓你退出社團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微借用一下葉太哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 花房君他..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有重要的事要單獨跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉昨天突然聯絡你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還把善後的事情全推給了你..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「幫」是爸爸搗毀的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有殘黨也全部逮捕歸案了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下他們就完全毀滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我留下的話 說不定那孩子就不會離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不知道希露比亞要找的就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 那孩子一直在躲著我 沒那麼容易抓到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和羽花羽炎一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子也曾淪為幫的犯罪工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果葉太沒有出手相助的話 恐怕她又會..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在搞什麼啊 爸爸明明把她的事托付給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來尋找那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太真善良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別太勉強了 希露比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝掛念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是爸爸托付給我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須完成才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我要去尋找玉鳳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太在騎士部好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事啊？花房君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他長年在國外生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可隨意和女生擁抱什麼的..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩人到底是什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇死我了 找我有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身都僵掉了..連一步都邁不動..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼騎士部..這根本不能叫社團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？真緒..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是個葉太郎還逞什麼強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 你能這麼努力很了不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我來幫你擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我才沒有客氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:03.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}冴同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你聽 電話響了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀吼 過得可好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別隨便叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳那傢伙 完全派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我就該這麼幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對冴同學做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 葉太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？看到了？就在剛剛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸..KnightLancer..玉鳳的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer那混蛋..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢傷了老大..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個戴奇怪面具的傢伙..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我親手來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要抓我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個變態和我沒有任何關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不知道啊 明明聽說你們關係不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把女士放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話 如果想要我放人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你放了這位女士 作為交換我可以任由你處置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是認真的 我要為老大報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把女士放了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說我是認真的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想對他射擊..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對KnightLancer..對爸爸..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開槍射擊..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要對爸爸開槍射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以..玉鳳要..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 你不能做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等等 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就為你鬆綁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的話 一定能拯救大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士 請原諒我的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你的善良 我已銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要追我 為什麼 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會來這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問希露比亞為什麼呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於遇上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斬..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如要妨礙..斬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？雖然不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現世騎士團的權天使希露比亞·瑪羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是經歷過無數腥風血雨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子也太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希露比亞 希露比亞 希露比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊？為什麼要做這種事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種傢伙..最好像你師父一樣被人殺死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被殺死？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父是因為生病..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的師父因為意圖背叛「幫」所以才..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師父是被殺的..師父是被殺的..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刺中了爸爸..玉鳳把爸爸..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淘氣過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼砍不中 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可著急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是到危急關頭 就越要沉心靜氣..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓自己擺脫一切雜念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳..壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把爸爸弄傷了 最愛的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer..師父..對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為你的父親 你遭遇危機之時我必會趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你..你到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受了這麼重的傷 你還想要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心愛的女兒受傷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為父親的我一定要全力保護好她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士不能空言虛語 這一點你明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長槍 衝鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 為了玉鳳..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.59,0:18:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你啊 依子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堪稱完美的應急處置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是比專家還厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有依子姐在 你就沒命了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冴同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子姐保護得好好的呢 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你真的對依子姐發出挑戰了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為..我想保護玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊 葉太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子姐啊 是因為你受傷才生氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不知爹媽苦心的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之這陣子好好聽依子姐的話 做個乖孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳她..還是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那時沒有逃走的話 她肯定會被依子姐殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 葉太你別想太多專心療傷就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你和玉鳳..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 大家也都認識玉鳳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看到她在哭泣 所以我就把她帶回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是和葉太郎那次一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您把素未相識的玉鳳就這麼帶回來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起這就是你的家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要住在這裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為玉鳳是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是KnightLancer的妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉鳳是KnightLancer的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼她當然也是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此..玉鳳她..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起玉鳳就是我的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 但是這孩子是壞蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這..這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像生氣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以欺負玉鳳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是欺負她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了壞事就一定要接受處罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只會嬌慣孩子的母親不是好母親哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 身為母親不能總是嬌慣孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然得到了真緒小姐的許可..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:10.01,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}今天開始是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
